# ============================================================
# AI 音乐电台 · Git 属性
# 统一换行符（根治 Windows 上每次 commit 的 LF→CRLF 警告）+ 二进制标记
# ============================================================

# 默认：文本文件仓库内统一存 LF，检出也用 LF（现代编辑器均支持）
* text=auto eol=lf

# Windows 脚本必须保持 CRLF（双击运行依赖）
*.bat text eol=crlf
*.ps1 text eol=crlf
*.cmd text eol=crlf

# 二进制文件：不做换行符转换、不计入文本 diff
*.mp3        binary
*.png        binary
*.jpg        binary
*.jpeg       binary
*.gif        binary
*.ico        binary
*.webp       binary
*.db         binary
*.sqlite3    binary
*.woff       binary
*.woff2      binary
*.ttf        binary
*.excalidraw binary
